Summary 



In addition to joining MacAndrews & Forbes Holdings Inc. in 1994, Mr. Savas serves as Executive Vice President and Chief Financial Officer of M & F Worldwide Corp. and sits on the boards of SIGA Technologies, Inc., Harland Clarke Holdings Corp., and TransTech Pharma, Inc.



