Director of Revlon (NYSE:REV), Savas Paul G, buys 8,100 shares worth $232,493
According to Revlon's most recent Form 4 filing with the SEC dated Nov 14 06:03 AM, company Director, Savas Paul G disclosed buying 8,100 shares at a cost of $28.70. At the time of this transaction (Nov 11), this trade was worth $232,493 in total. As of Nov 11, Savas Paul G now owns 27,900 shares in total worth about $820,260.0. 
